an Gunatilake]] {{post-nominals|FRCP}} <small>[[Ceylon College of Physicians|FCCP]]</small> \u2013 Professor of Medicine, [[University of Sri Jayewardenepura]]<ref name=\"Saman\">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2002/01/07/new13.html |title=Induction ceremony of the President |publisher=Dailynews.lk |date=2002-01-07 |accessdate=2011-09-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604234155/http://www.dailynews.lk/2002/01/07/new13.html |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref> (note: also listed in Medicine)\n* [[Nalin de Silva]] \u2013 Professor of Mathematics, Department of Mathematics, [[University of Kelaniya]]\n* [[Suri Ratnapala|A. Suri Ratnapala]] \u2013 Professor of Law, T.C. Beirne School of Law, [[University of Queensland]]\n* [[Nihal Jayawickrama]] \u2013 former Professor of Law at [[University of Hong Kong]] and Ariel F Sallows Professor of Human Rights at [[University of Saskatchewan]] (note: also listed in lawyers)\n* [[D. N. Samarasekera]] {{post-nominals|FRCS}} \u2013 Professor of Surgery, Head of the Department of Surgery, University of Colombo<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rcclassof72.lk/old_site/inside_pages/d.htm |title=Samarasekera Dharmabandhu Nandadeva Dr |publisher=Rcclassof72.lk |date= |accessdate=2011-09-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/medicine/ext_pages/surgery/samarasekara.htm |title=Prof. D.N.Samarasekera |publisher=Cmb.ac.lk |date=2005-12-08 |accessdate=2012-02-23 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301165746/http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/medicine/ext_pages/surgery/samarasekara.htm |archivedate=2012-03-01 }}</ref>\n* [[Chandima Gomes]] \u2013 Professor of Electrical Engineering, [[Universiti Putra Malaysia]] and Head of the Centre for Electromagnetic and Lightning Protection Malaysia<ref>[[Chandima Gomes]]</ref>\n* [[R. K. W. Goonesekera]] \u2013 Professor of Law, [[Ahmadu Bello University]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sundaytimes.lk/980405/news5.html |title=VIP Complex p