va, Ph.D |publisher=Lirneasia.net |date=1999-02-22 |accessdate=2011-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306060518/http://lirneasia.net/profiles/harsha-desilva/ |archive-date=2009-03-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Faiszer|Musthapha}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] \u2013 former State Minister \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Harshana|Rajakaruna}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Imran|Maharoof}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Kavinda|Jayawardena}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] \n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Malik|Samarawickrama}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] \u2013 Minister of Development Strategies and International Trade\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Mayantha|Dissanayake}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|}\n\n;Opposition benches\n* [[Dinesh Gunawardena]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 former Cabinet Minister of National Water Supply and current Member of Parliament\n* [[Arumugam Thondaman]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 former Cabinet Minister of Livestock and Rural Community Development; current Member of Parliament\n* [[Mahindananda Aluthgamage]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 former Cabinet Minister of Sports and current Member of Parliament\n* [[Anuradha Jayaratne]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 current Member of Parliament\n* [[Kanchana Wijesekera]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 current Member of Parliament\n* [[M. A. Sumanthiran]] <small>[[Parliament of Sri Lanka|MP]]</small> \u2013 current Member of Parliament\n\n====Former====\n;Post-Independence\n* [[Sir]] [[Frank Gunasekera]] \u2013 Depu