 welcome new Appeal Court President, Justices]</ref><ref>[http://www.fbc.com.fj/fiji/6482/appeal-for-rape-conviction Appeal for rape conviction]</ref>\n* [[Achala Wengappuli]] \u2013 current Judge of the Court of Appeal of Sri Lanka\n\n;Other judges\n* [[Sarath Ambepitiya]] \u2013 former Judge of the [[High Court of Sri Lanka|High Court of Colombo]]\n* [[J. R. Weinman]] \u2013 former [[District Courts of Sri Lanka|District Judge]] of Colombo (note: also listed in Legislators)\n* [[Charles Ambrose Lorensz]] \u2013 former District Judge, Acting Queen's Advocate (note: also listed in Legislators and journalists)\n* [[Dhammika Kitulgoda]] \u2013 District Judge (note: also listed in Civil servants)\n\n==Provincial and local government==\n===Governors===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:*;\" | Name\n! style=\"width:65%;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notability\n! style=\"width:*;\" class=\"unsortable\" | Reference(s)\n|-\n| {{sortname|Nalin|Seneviratne}}\n| [[Lieutenant General]] [[Commander of the Army (Sri Lanka)|Commander of the Army]] (1985&ndash;1988), [[List of Governors of North Eastern Province|Governor of North East Province]] (1988&ndash;1993)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |\n|-\n| {{sortname|Tyronne|Fernando}}\n| [[Parliament of Sri Lanka|Member of Parliament]] for [[Moratuwa Electoral District|Moratuwa]] (1977&ndash;1989), [[List of Governors of North Eastern Province|Governor of North East Province]] (1993&ndash;1994)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref name=\"E.F.C. Pereira\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2008/02/27/news18.asp |title=Tyronne Fernando dead |publisher=Dailynews.lk |accessdate=2011-09-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080302000455/http://www.dailynews.lk/2008/02/27/news18.asp |archivedate=2008-03-02 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{sortname|Neville|Kanakeratne}}\n| [[List of Governors of Southern Province|Governor of Southern Province]] (1995&ndash;1999)\n| style=\"text-align:center