te       = 14 January 2020\n}}\n\n'''Kanarin Thawornsak''' ({{lang-th|\u0e01\u0e32\u0e19\u0e15\u0e4c\u0e19\u0e23\u0e34\u0e19\u0e17\u0e23\u0e4c \u0e16\u0e32\u0e27\u0e23\u0e28\u0e31\u0e01\u0e14\u0e34\u0e4c}}, born May 27, 1997), is a Thai professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder (association football)#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Thai League 1]] club [[Port F.C.|Port]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/kannarin-thawornsak/439163/|title=Kanarin Thawornsak Profile|date=|website=Soccerway}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nIn 2020, He played the [[2020 AFC U-23 Championship]] with [[Thailand national under-23 football team|Thailand U23]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/kannarin-thawornsak/439163/ |title=K. Thawornsak - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway |website=us.soccerway.com |date=2013-01-09 |accessdate=2016-12-04}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Thongsong, Suphan}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Suphan Buri Province]]\n[[Category:Thai footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football central defenders]]\n[[Category:Police Tero F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Thai League 1 players]]\n[[Category:Thai League 2 players]]\n\n\n{{Thailand-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Thai footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Kanarin Thawornsak\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Kanarin Thawornsak\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1997|05|27|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Ratchaburi Province|Ratchaburi]], [[Thailand]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| currentclub    = [[Port F.C.|Port]]\n| clubnumber     = 31\n| position       = [[Midfielder (association football)#Defensive midfielder|Defensive midfielder]]\n| youthyears1    = 2012\u20132014\n| youthclubs1    = [[Bangkok Christia